<h4 id="amalfi-coast">Amalfi coast</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Agerola: Picchio Rosso  - Spaghetti Vongole - Our culinary journey continued along the picturesque Amalfi coast, where we indulged in Picchio Rosso’s delightful spaghetti vongole, a taste of the Mediterranean breeze.</li>
</ul>

<p>
